Description: This package infers package usage from either saved files or through an active listener. Scan files using `pkg_scan()` or listen to evaluated code by adding `pkgusage::listen()` to your `.Rprofile`. Then use helper functions to extract usage and compare to the installed packages to detect unused or missing packages.
